subject: Dear Sir,
body:
Dear Sir,
I understand you didn't have passport. I need you to send me any of your photo ID via email attachment.
Regards.

subject: Re:   Dear Sir,
body:
Hello,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I appreciate your concern about my passport. However, I'm a bit hesitant to share my personal information online. Can you please provide more details about why you need my photo ID? 

I look forward to hearing from you.

Best wishes,
George
